title: PARMA BEAUTY
posting_body: ['HOUSE DESCRIPTION:', 'Quiet, children-friendly side street, 2 blocks away from elementary school.', ' Beautiful & inviting brick bungalow in the hart of Parma off Pearl & Snow, 6 min.', 'drive to I-480.', '  Three bedrooms (2 on first level), updated kitchen & bath, hardwood floors throughout, full clean and dry basement with finished rec.', 'room, 2 car garage with door openers, privacy fenced and gated back-yard, central air.', 'We need tenants who will appreciate and maintain this beautiful house, and who are planning to rent it long-term.', ' Rented directly by owner.', 'TERMS:', 'Available to move in September 1st 2022.', ' One year lease agreement, $1,300/month plus security deposit.', ' Pets are extra.', ' $38 fee for background check (refundable if
